When writing or editing Golang, you must follow these style rules.

## Use modern loops
Do not write
```go
for i := 0; i < num; i++ {
		...
}
```
Instead write
```go
for range num {
    ...
}
```

## Do not initialise rand
There is no need to call rand.Seed
